quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  26,160,"Abandu ba Luti bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,161,"Olwa Omusiani wabu (ulangwa mbu) Luti yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimuritsanga tawe?"
  26,162,"Toto esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa omwisikwa."
  26,163,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,164,"Ne shindenyakhwo omurungo khu kano tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,165,"Koo, mubiloonje bioosi mukholanga eshifwolo abasaatsa khubasatsa?"
  26,166,"Ne mulekhanga shia Nyasaye wenyu yabaloonjela khubakhasi benyu? Toto enywe muli abandu babura eshichelo.”"
  26,167,"Baboola mbu: “Ewe Lut, nolalekhana ninafu tawe, olaba mubalia abalatafibwa.”"
  26,168,"Naboola mbu: “Esie toto endi mubasinyisibwa muno nende eshikhole shienyu esho.""
  26,169,"Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, habina esie nende Abandu banje okhurulana nende akabakholanga kano.""
  26,170,"Mana nikhumuhabina ye nende Abandu bebe boosi."
  26,171,"Halali Omushiele khubalia abekhalanga inyuma."
  26,172,"Mana nikhusishia abandi abo."
  26,173,"Mana nikhubakwisilia ifula, ne ni ifula imbii muno ya balia bekanyilisibwa."
  26,174,"Toto mukano kalimwo ameeko, halali abaanji mubo shibasuubilanga tawe."
  26,175,"Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Owamaani, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  26,176,"Abandu bomutsuru omukhongo bayingasia Abarumwa."
  26,177,"Olwa Shuwaib yababoolela mbu: “Koo, shimuritsangakhwo Nyasaye tawe?"
  26,178,"Toto Esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa Omwisikwa."
  26,179,"Kho rie Nyasaye, ne muwulile esie."
  26,180,"Ne shebasabaanga khu kano omurungo kwosikwosi tawe. Omurungo kwanje kuli sa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  26,181,"Itsusie eshichelo obulayi, ne mulaba mubalia baleeminjia tawe."
  26,182,"Ne chele khushichelo shili habwene."
  26,183,"Ne mulaleemilia Abandu ebindu biabu tawe, ne mulachenda khushialo nimukhola obwonooni tawe."